headline: Does PayPal Stock Look Poised for a Turnaround?
summary: PayPal is looking to transform itself into a commerce platform.  The company showed solid signs of a turnaround in Q1.  PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL) has had a tough start to 2025, with its shares down more than 20%.
